{"ID":"20260609124420-6ggespr","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609124420-6ggespr","title":"2023年新高考Ⅱ卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609124435-4k1cw16","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124435-4k1cw16","updated":"20260609124435"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“耳机一戴，谁也不爱”。周围的世界有时太嘈杂了，但想安静一下不被打扰也很容易，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":" ① "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。可是最近，樊女士发现，自从经常戴上耳机听着歌入睡以来，耳朵里开始有了“嗡嗡嗡”的耳鸣声。去医院一看，居然是过度使用耳机造成的突发性耳聋。那么，使用耳机"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":" ② "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"？医学研究告诉我们，这个度包括时间和音量两方面，即音量不宜超过最大音量的60%，时间要限制在60分钟以内。如果超过这个限度，就可能威胁耳朵的健康。比如诱发耳部炎症，导致耳朵疼痛、耳屎变多等。有人觉得这都是小事，忍忍就过去了。但事实上，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"③ "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，还可能逐渐升级。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124435-gb71ln7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124435-gb71ln7","updated":"20260609124435"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对耳朵来说，过大的声音就是噪音，噪音会对耳道产生压力，压力又会撞击鼓膜听骨链传到内耳，震荡前庭淋巴液，这一系列连锁反应下来，会出现晕车一样的头晕症状。声音过大还会损坏耳蜗中的听觉毛细胞，导致耳鸣。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"如果长时间暴露在过大的声音中，会使听觉毛细胞失去敏感性，无法接收声音的信号，形成暂时或永久性听力下降。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124455-7nueuxf","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609124455-7nueuxf","updated":"20260609124456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609124435-3w7epag","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124435-3w7epag","updated":"20260609124435"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．下列句子中的“谁”和“耳机一戴，谁也不爱”中的“谁”，意义和用法相同的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609124435-hbt70y8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124435-hbt70y8","updated":"20260609124435"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．怅寥廓，问苍茫大地，谁主沉浮？"}]},{"ID":"20260609124435-mxhlm68","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124435-mxhlm68","updated":"20260609124435"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．生活中谁都需要表达和交流。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124435-sylc3d6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124435-sylc3d6","updated":"20260609124435"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．我本来是跟他开玩笑的，谁知道他竟然生气了。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124435-rfpglrc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124435-rfpglrc","updated":"20260609124435"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．我越来越深刻地感觉到谁是我们最可爱的人！"}]},{"ID":"20260609124435-zfsff5r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124435-zfsff5r","updated":"20260609124435"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"21．请在文中横线处补写恰当的语句，使整段文字语意完整连贯，内容贴切，逻辑严密，每处不超过10个字。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124435-9vy7luo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124435-9vy7luo","updated":"20260609124435"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"22．文中画波浪线的部分有语病，请进行修改，使语言表达准确流畅。可增删少量词语，但不得改变原意。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124503-8vnaycm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609124503-8vnaycm","updated":"20260609124520"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609124520-r09rbqv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124520-r09rbqv","updated":"20260609124520"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．B    21．①你只需要一副耳机  ②有什么限度  ③过度使用耳机的危害    22．如果长时间暴露在过大的声音中，听觉毛细胞会失去敏感性，无法接收声音的信号，导致暂时或永久性听力下降。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124506-jrdvgve","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609124506-jrdvgve","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-87gqxpl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-87gqxpl","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．本题考查学生正确使用词语的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-4bfkzjb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-4bfkzjb","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"疑问代词“谁”的用法分为基本用法和特殊用法。基本用法表示疑问，特殊用法有非疑问用法，非疑问用法有任指、虚指和定指。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-nvqztht","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-nvqztht","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“耳机一戴，谁也不爱”中的“谁”表示任指，指任何人。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-rpv2snt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-rpv2snt","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A. 表示疑问，“谁主沉浮”中“谁”指什么人。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-kdf5atz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-kdf5atz","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B. 表示任指，“谁都需要表达和交流”中“谁”是指任何人。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-rqvl0ie","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-rqvl0ie","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C. 表示虚指，“谁知道他竟然生气了”中“谁”是指表示不能肯定的人。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-kl02u2e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-kl02u2e","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D. 表示定指，“谁是我们最可爱的人”中“谁”是指说话者和听话者双方都十分确定的人。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-byxajrm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-byxajrm","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"据以上分析看出B项与例句意义和用法相同。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-ai2cxx5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-ai2cxx5","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-2gxtbze","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-2gxtbze","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"21．本题考查学生情境补写的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-pi1ngnu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-pi1ngnu","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一空，根据前文“‘耳机一戴，谁也不爱’。周围的世界有时太嘈杂了，但想安静一下不被打扰也很容易”，可看出是在说明戴上耳机可以安静下来不被打扰，所以可填“你只需要一副耳机”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-6j2bnau","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-6j2bnau","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二空，根据后文“医学研究告诉我们，这个度包括时间和音量两方面，……如果超过这个限度，就可能威胁耳朵的健康”，可知是说使用耳机的限度，又联系语境“那么，使用耳机 ？”，此处应是一个问句，所以可填“有什么限度”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-9fl8slt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-9fl8slt","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第三空，根据前文“如果超过这个限度，就可能威胁耳朵的健康。比如诱发耳部炎症，导致耳朵疼痛、耳屎变多等。有人觉得这都是小事，忍忍就过去了”，再结合语境“但事实上， ，还可能逐渐升级”，可看出是说过度使用耳机对耳朵有损伤，所以可填“过度使用耳机的危害”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-7xsj0on","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-7xsj0on","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"22．本题考查学生辨析并修改病句的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-ztcdv6q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-ztcdv6q","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"画线句语病有两处："}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-c07die1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-c07die1","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一是成分残缺，“会使听觉毛细胞失去敏感性，无法接收声音的信号”缺少主语，可去掉“会使”，让“听觉毛细胞”作主语。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-m5aw48w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-m5aw48w","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"二是搭配不当，“形成”与“听力下降”不搭配，可改为“导致暂时或永久性听力下降”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124531-elmtqda","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124531-elmtqda","updated":"20260609124531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故改为：如果长时间暴露在过大的声音中，听觉毛细胞会失去敏感性，无法接收声音的信号，导致暂时或永久性听力下降。"}]}]}